{"Id":463254,"Title":"浣溪沙","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"张恨水","Context":"自把琅环当百城。浪书尘事遣浮生。从来小技易成名。莫道聪明能误我，误人正是半聪明。琴书为我也飘零。欲道升平一语难。樽前何况是阳关。隔帘人去影姗姗。古调不须悲白雪，风尘无处觅黄衫。千秋难铲恨如山。大半闲情恋夕晖。当年张绪景全非。笑啼不是只填词。席上笙歌今夜梦，眼前花事暮春泥。老天犹遣子规啼。海外人疑是老儒。少年豪气想萧疏。再休风雨病相如。浊酒化为知己泪，新诗吟作绝交书。解人虽有不如无。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浣溪沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"5dd65b0b6af9da854bc903676ddaae49","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5155913,"Sentence":"自把琅环当百城。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zì bǎ láng huán dāng bǎi chéng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155914,"Sentence":"浪书尘事遣浮生。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"làng shū chén shì qiǎn fú shēng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155915,"Sentence":"从来小技易成名。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cóng lái xiǎo jì yì chéng mǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155917,"Sentence":"琴书为我也飘零。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qǐn shū wéi wǒ yě piāo lǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155918,"Sentence":"欲道升平一语难。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yù dāo shēng pǐng yī yǔ nán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155919,"Sentence":"樽前何况是阳关。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zūn qián hé kuàng shì yáng guān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155920,"Sentence":"隔帘人去影姗姗。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gé lián rén qù ying shān shān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155921,"Sentence":"古调不须悲白雪，风尘无处觅黄衫。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gǔ diào bú xū bēi bái xuě ，fēng chén mó chǔ mì huáng shān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5155922,"Sentence":"千秋难铲恨如山。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiān qīu nán chǎn hèn rú shān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"So